{"tid":1898294,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[突發] Alistair Carmichael 提出私人議案後, 小粉紅已經準備破壞","createTime":"2020-02-26T04:46:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-26T13:02:06.000Z","uid":226304,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ea6c79d8177b4a08e5b0bb38b5a040a9fccc08f4","tid":1898294,"uid":226304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T04:46:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.pincong.rocks/article/15217\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pincong.rocks%2Farticle%2F15217&d=RwLhzhYA7Smtfd5%2FYaS6XyZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=3c1820b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pincong.rocks/article/15217</a><br />\n[BNO事件]有關海外反共的行動建議<br />\n近日英國議員阿利斯泰爾&middot;卡邁克爾在英國國會上提出讓持有BNO護照的香港人獲得居英權的轉移。在下議院已經獲得首讀通過，等待6月12日二讀。<br />\n<br />\n我看了一下BNO的維基百科，原來這個是於1980年代因香港前途問題而設立，讓香港的英國屬土公民申請，擊敗他們在香港主權移交以後，繼續與英國保持某種關係。而你(中)國 只承認英國國民（海外）護照為旅遊證件。具你(中)國血統，並在香港或中國出生的英國國民（海外），都被視為你(中)國公民。<br />\n<br />\n我感覺這個初步很可能會引起小粉紅的反彈<br />\n<br />\n我建議先在小粉紅圈子提高這個話題的熱度，最理想的結果是他們到英國的推特，臉書鬧事，而且在6月12日在國會持中國國旗抗議。這樣的話很可能會引起跟英國 人的矛盾，有助英國在華為等雙邊上立場更強硬。<br />\n<br />\n議案影片<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Nwh1od6TZuE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DNwh1od6TZuE&d=RwLhzhYA7Smtfd5%2FYaS6XyZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=6b85a20a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Nwh1od6TZuE</a>"},{"pid":"bdff383a7a716d269783e1c0b2a57ec9b2a71a8c","tid":1898294,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T04:47:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f399f3c20084309b52332287797c64ef51dbc85","tid":1898294,"uid":76365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T11:56:02.000Z","msg":"姐係英國版612？"},{"pid":"d43d5c452784286472482715e7be4afe3dba6979","tid":1898294,"uid":91721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T12:00:36.000Z","msg":"呢個唔係反共網嚟嘅咩？"},{"pid":"dc692bf2a49dfdda88be67c1ea404ebc68c54950","tid":1898294,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T12:01:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dfdcd59b1d1efb704c034258d8eb93f50a5267e","tid":1898294,"uid":4917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T12:03:47.000Z","msg":"反咩彈，英國處理佢國家內部國籍問題關中國鳩事"},{"pid":"68c79cd9115e9f145139d9f524732bb279639cf4","tid":1898294,"uid":34213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T12:59:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"612dff28d1792070936fa87a41e78d55beb8e1ea","tid":1898294,"uid":115212,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T13:02:06.000Z","msg":"如果班小粉紅衝出嚟7又唔錯啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}